item.title: How Do i Make Normal Pest ctrl?
item.dc:creator: @davidi2 Davidi2
item.description:
@davidi2 wrote:

LOL! WOW. it is a long process.

  1. Use a interface maker to create the interface. Youd need to download all of the sprites to. (10-30 mins)
  2. Create the ints in your client and add them. (5-10 mins)
  3. Configure all of actionbuttons, ect, and add them to server. (10-20 mins)

That seems like a while to me just for one interface.
